nodes.text: Warrin Station was a location that was a popular haunt for smugglers following the Battle of Endor. Han Solo and Chewbacca rallied several smugglers and Wookiee exiles there as part of their campaign to liberate the Wookiee homeworld of Kashyyyk. While searching for Han, Norra Wexley and her team learned that Solo was last sighted at Warrin Station.
